          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-body mb-3">4. Prohibited Use</h2>
          <p class="text-muted">
            You agree not to use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in any way that violates applicable local, national, or international laws or regulations. This includes, but is not limited to:
